{"version":"0.4","title":"n 4","type":"page","content":[{"id":"205cf6b9","settings":[],"elements":[{"id":"508c7b32","settings":{"_column_size":100},"elements":[{"id":"64ffc251","settings":{"editor":"<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>principles of reggio<\/h2>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3><strong>THE IMAGE OF THE CHILD <\/strong>&nbsp;<\/h3>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Children as competent individuals with unique perspectives, experiences and interests.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3><strong>ENVIRONMENT AS THE THIRD TEACHER<\/strong><\/h3>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The furniture and materials in the room are intentionally placed to inspire curiosity and provide opportunities to learn<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3><strong>RELATIONSHIPS<\/strong><\/h3>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The importance of all relationships and interactions involving the children\u2019s lives; this includes but is not limited to families, teachers and children.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3><strong>COLLABORATION<\/strong><\/h3>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Teamwork is encouraged.&nbsp;Children, families, parents, teachers and the community collaborate to provide an optimal learning environment.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3><strong>PROVOCATION<\/strong><\/h3>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our teachers listen closely to the children and devise numerous ways to provoke further thought and action. They ask open-ended questions to better understand the children\u2019s schema and promote further investigations.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\" id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1611913281599_832\"><img src=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/5af21e3c25bf02e7690fb9fe\/1580778070546-CZZT2J2MFP4NI43427DP\/ke17ZwdGBToddI8pDm48kHH9S2ID7_bpupQnTdrPcoF7gQa3H78H3Y0txjaiv_0fDoOvxcdMmMKkDsyUqMSsMWxHk725yiiHCCLfrh8O1z4YTzHvnKhyp6Da-NYroOW3ZGjoBKy3azqku80C789l0nQwvinDXPV4EYh2MRzm-RRB5rUELEv7EY2n0AZOrEupxpSyqbqKSgmzcCPWV5WMiQ\/_DSC1262%25281%2529.jpg?format=750w\" alt=\"_DSC1262%281%29.jpg\"\/><\/figure>\n<!-- \/wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\" id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1611913281599_851\"><img src=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/5af21e3c25bf02e7690fb9fe\/1529002775703-QLT19OPMC4JW2CI7YM8F\/ke17ZwdGBToddI8pDm48kLkXF2pIyv_F2eUT9F60jBl7gQa3H78H3Y0txjaiv_0fDoOvxcdMmMKkDsyUqMSsMWxHk725yiiHCCLfrh8O1z4YTzHvnKhyp6Da-NYroOW3ZGjoBKy3azqku80C789l0iyqMbMesKd95J-X4EagrgU9L3Sa3U8cogeb0tjXbfawd0urKshkc5MgdBeJmALQKw\/_DSC1347%281%29.jpg?format=750w\" alt=\"_DSC1347(1).jpg\"\/><\/figure>\n<!-- \/wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3><strong>PROGETTAZIONE<\/strong>&nbsp;(LONG-TERM PROJECTS)<\/h3>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>These are flexible plans for the further investigation of ideas and interests.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3><strong>ONE HUNDRED LANGUAGES OF CHILDREN<\/strong><\/h3>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We believe children have more than 100 ways of expressing themselves. It is our responsibility to provide them with as much variety in materials as possible for them to express themselves.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3><strong>TRANSPARENCY<\/strong><\/h3>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We embrace transparency,&nbsp;In the sense of open floor plans and transparent containers to house materials whenever possible. Additionally, there is transparency in communication with the parents and openness to other cultures and communities.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3><strong>DOCUMENTATION<\/strong><\/h3>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Teachers document the process children choose to take during their projects. Observations and verbal conversations are written down, photos of the children at work as well as artifacts the children produce are included in the final documentation piece. These factors are discussed, interpreted and displayed in each classroom to show the learning that has occurred.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>benefits<\/h2>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>PAID HOLIDAYS<\/h3>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>PAID FAMILY WEEKS<\/h3>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>CONTINUING EDUCATION&nbsp;<\/h3>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>CLASSROOM BUDGET<\/h3>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>STAFF DEVELOPMENT DAYS<\/h3>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>STAFF EVENTS<\/h3>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>MEDICAL INSURANCE<\/h3>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>DENTAL INSURANCE<\/h3>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>VISION INSURANCE<\/h3>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>SUPPLEMENTAL INSURANCE<\/h3>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>PAID SICK TIME&nbsp;<\/h3>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>PAID TIME OFF<\/h3>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>*FOR REGULAR FULL TIME EMPLOYEES<\/h3>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\" id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1611913281599_870\"><img src=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/5af21e3c25bf02e7690fb9fe\/1592009144963-DHHDA00FR38KQJ77TOY3\/ke17ZwdGBToddI8pDm48kKAwwdAfKsTlKsCcElEApLR7gQa3H78H3Y0txjaiv_0fDoOvxcdMmMKkDsyUqMSsMWxHk725yiiHCCLfrh8O1z5QPOohDIaIeljMHgDF5CVlOqpeNLcJ80NK65_fV7S1UegTYNQkRo-Jk4EWsyBNhwKrKLo5CceA1-Tdpfgyxoog5ck0MD3_q0rY3jFJjjoLbQ\/_DSC1992.jpg?format=750w\" alt=\"_DSC1992.jpg\"\/><\/figure>\n<!-- \/wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"column"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"section"},{"id":"77d105b8","settings":[],"elements":[{"id":"6d8b5570","settings":{"_column_size":100,"_inline_size":null},"elements":[{"id":"5720e9ee","settings":{"social_icon_list":[{"social_icon":{"value":"fab fa-facebook","library":"fa-brands"},"_id":"f0fc7ab"},{"social_icon":{"value":"fab fa-twitter","library":"fa-brands"},"_id":"80a8cce"},{"social_icon":{"value":"fab fa-youtube","library":"fa-brands"},"_id":"d9e9735"}],"shape":"circle","_animation":"fadeInRight"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"social-icons","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"column"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"section"}]}